# MarketplaceV3DirectListings.getAll() method

Get all direct listings

## Example

```javascript

```

**Signature:**

```typescript

```

| Parameter | Type                                            | Description                             |

| filter    | [MarketplaceFilter](./sdk.marketplacefilter.md) | _(Optional)_ optional filter parameters |
